  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "synopsis",
      "abstract": "This Act requires the Division of Public Health to submit a report to various government officials and post on its website the data it receives from schools regarding the number of kindergartners who meet the requirements under this chapter for screening for lead poisoning."
